-- El Cedro Barcelona - English-Speaking Dental Clinic specializing in implantology and dental tourism
('El Cedro Barcelona', 'Dental', 'English-speaking dental clinic in Barcelona''s Eixample district, specializing in implantology and dental surgery. Founded in 2000 by Dr. Olivier Bournay and now led by Dr. Leticia Rodriguez (23+ years experience, registered with Order of Dentists of Barcelona nº2587), the clinic has been welcoming international patients since 2013. Full English-speaking team including patient coordinators, dental surgeons, assistants and hygienists who also speak Spanish and French. Specializes in dental implants (using Nobel Biocare, GC AADVA, Global D and Straumann brands), bone grafting, complete oral rehabilitation, prosthetic treatments (crowns, bridges), dental whitening, and oral surgery. Offers conscious sedation administered by specialized anesthesiologists for patient comfort. Features an in-house prosthesis laboratory ensuring quality and traceability. Provides patients with an "implant passport" for full transparency and post-treatment follow-up. Conveniently located near Sagrada Familia in central Barcelona. Open Monday to Friday 9:00-13:00 and 15:00-19:00, Saturday by prior appointment. Popular choice for dental tourism patients from France, UK and worldwide seeking high-quality, affordable dental care.', 'Carrer de Girona 108, 08009 Barcelona', 'Barcelona', 'Barcelona', '+34 933 15 59 93', NULL, 'https://www.elcedrobarcelona.com/en/', true, false, true, false, NOW(), NOW());
